description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Coffee With SCREAMER Edition with Jessica Freeburg

Oh sure, when you need a little pick me up, there is nothing like caffeine to get you going, but how about a fright or a laugh?! Tim and Jessica are rushing around and brewing up the Supernatural headlines that you are looking for this week!

This week,  Robert Bigelow has some big cash waiting for you if you can scientifically prove there is life after death, The Navy says NOT SO FAST on that disclosure thing, A coffee house in Logan, Utah is brewing up some spooky spirits, and we meet Loab, the freakish AI art woman who is haunting the internet!!

Take a look at what "Loab" looks like here:   https://www.cnet.com/science/what-is-loab-the-haunting-ai-art-woman-explained/

Get Jessica Freeburg's book, Monsters of the Midwest, here:  https://amzn.to/3BFQYkE
